# Performance

- Never block API with AI or file parsing — use BullMQ workers.
- Lazy-load heavy frontend components (charts, kanban, GSAP).
- TanStack Query staleTime to reduce redundant fetches.
- Target excellent Core Web Vitals on landing and dashboard.
- Turborepo caching for CI builds.
- Prisma: select only needed fields; avoid N+1 with includes.
- Redis connection pooling for BullMQ.
